'''Kubazian skirts''' were non-gender specific garments that came from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kubindi/Legends|Kubindi]]. [[Mustafarian/Legends|Mustafarians]], who looked very similar to the [[Kubaz/Legends|Kubaz]], were often seen wearing these skirts while harvesting lava on their [[Mustafar/Legends|planet]].

The skirts were equipped with a cooling backpack-turbine, which aided in keeping the species from suffering heat exhaustion.

